3. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper's focus on accurately representing the geometry of man-made environments could be relevant to graphics applications such as virtual reality or video game design.

5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper's focus on developing a novel method for extracting polylines from laser range scans could be considered an artificial intelligence problem.
